Umcimbi kumele ube usenzeka manje, futhi kumele ube ngaphakathi kwendawo yegagasi yomcimbi. Bheka i-FAQ ngezinketho zokulingisa.
Uqinisekile ufuna ukususa le mephu? Ungayilanda futhi kamuva uma kudingeka.
Le mephu ayikwazi ukususwa ngoba iyingxenye yohlelo lokusebenza oluyisisekelo noma iyadingwa ezinye izici. Izosuswa uma ususa uhlelo lokusebenza.
Awekho imicimbi eyengezwe ekuthandwayo, qala ngokuchofoza isithonjana senkanyezi emcimbini owuthandayo!
Kubukeka sengathi i-GPS yakho icishiwe, uyafuna ukuyivula?
Uyakwazi lokhu : uma indaba yoMhlaba ibingalandiswa encwadini yamakhasi ayi-1,000, isintu besingavela kuphela esigabeni sokugcina sekhasi lokugcina.

Kodwa le ndaba emfushane ingaphela ngokushesha kunokulindelwe. Siwodwana emkhathini omkhulu nowugwadule. Sibhidliza konke. Siyazicabangela thina kuphela. Sinonya. Sinobugovu. Siyizimpumputhe. Futhi sifuna ukubusa. Kodwa futhi siyakwazi ukuzwelana, sakha izimangaliso, siyamelana nobunzima, singazidela.
Kodwa asinawo isikhathi esiningi. Senze inqubekelaphambili enkulu.. Singakha enye indlela : umphakathi wamalungelo, wobumbano, wentando yeningi. Kusezandleni zethu!

Joyina umkhankaso womhlaba, ukuvuka ngokuthula. Ake sakhe amagagasi abantu, ubufakazi bobuntu bethu bangempela, umlayezo oqinile kubaholi bethu. Ake sihlangane emadolobheni nasemazweni, emhlabeni wonke. Ake sikhethe ukuthula. Ake sikhethe injabulo. Ake sikhethe imvelo. Ake sikhethe THINA.
Kwenzeka kanjani uma igagasi elilodwa nje lanele ukusihlanganisa?

WorldWideWaves iyuhlelo lokusebenza lweselula lwesikhashana olunenjongo ebheka phambili: ukuhlela uchungechunge lwamagagasi abantu adlula emadolobheni amakhulu, awele amazwe. Kuzokwenzeka phakathi konyaka owodwa, lo mzamo uhlose ukudlula imingcele yezindawo namasiko, ukhuthaze umuzwa wobunye, umphakathi, nolwazi oluhlanganyelwayo.
Enhliziyweni yalo, i-WorldWideWaves akusona nje uhlelo lokusebenza, kuwunyakazo womhlaba wonke owenzelwe ukuhlanganisa abantu ekubonakaleni kobumbano nenjabulo, ngamagugu abelwana ngawo.
Ngokusebenzisa ubuchwepheshe, i-WorldWideWaves izokwenza ababambiqhaza emhlabeni wonke bakwazi ukujoyina la magagasi abantu emadolobheni abo, bedala umbukwane obonakalayo nowemizwa onamandla.

Ngamafuphi, i-WorldWideWaves uwumzamo onenkani wokusebenzisa amandla obuchwepheshe ngenhloso ehloniphekile, ukuhlanganisa isintu ekugubheni ubunye, injabulo nesenzo esihlangene. Ngamagagasi ngamunye, ababambiqhaza ngeke nje banikele kumbukwane womhlaba kodwa bazowuzwa futhi bawabelane nomhlaba umthelela ojulile wokuhlangana njengobunye.
Siyakwamukela ku-WorldWideWaves! Siyajabula ukukwamukela emicimbini yamagagasi omhlaba. Ukuze wonke umuntu abe nolwazi oluphephile nolumnandi, sicela ulandele le miyalelo:

Inhlonipho Kubo Bonke: Phatha bonke ababambiqhaza ngenhlonipho, kungakhathaliseki imvelaphi yabo. Sicela ugcine inhlonipho kubo bonke ababekhona; ukuziphatha ngokucwasa noma ukuhlukumeza akwamukelekile.
Hlonipha Izikhala Zomphakathi: Gcina izindlela zivulekile, landela imithetho nemibhalo yasendaweni, futhi ugweme ukuvimba ithrafikhi noma ukufinyelela kwezimo eziphuthumayo.
Hlala Ezindaweni Ezimisiwe: Ngokuphepha kwakho, hlala ngaphakathi ezindaweni ezimakwe zomcimbi uma zikhona.
Ziphendulele: Uma ukhetha ukuphuza, yenza lokho ngokulinganisela nangokuhambisana nemithetho yasendaweni.
Nciphisa Umthelela Emvelweni: Lahla yonke imfucumfucu ezitsheni ezibekelwe lokho futhi ugweme ukulahla phansi ukuze izindawo zihlanzeke.
Bika Okukhathazayo: Uma ubona okuthusayo noma othile osenkingeni, shesha ubikele iziphathimandla zendawo.
Gqoka Kahle: Gqoka izingubo nezicathulo ezikahle ezifanele imisebenzi yomcimbi nezimo zesimo sezulu.
Hlala Uphethwe Amanzi: Letha amanzi futhi uhlale uphuzile, ikakhulukazi emicimbini ezindaweni ezifudumele.
Qaphela Izimpahla Zakho: Gcina izimpahla zakho ziphephile futhi ugweme ukuletha izinto eziyigugu ongazidingi.
Sebenzisa Uhlelo Lobungani: Hlala nabangani noma wenze abasha, nibhekelane ukuphepha.
Lungela Izimo Eziphuthumayo: Londoloza izinombolo zezimo eziphuthumayo zendawo kucingo futhi vumelanani indawo yokuhlangana nabangani uma nehlukanisana.

Hlala Unokuqaphela: Khomba izindlela eziseduze eziphephile zokuphuma nezikhala ezivulekile (isb., izikwele, amapaki) ezikuzungezile, ulandele imiyalo yeziphathimandla zasendaweni uma kuvela isimo esiphuthumayo.
Oxhumana nabo Ezimo Eziphuthumayo: Londoloza inombolo yezimo eziphuthumayo yendawo okuyo kanye noxhumana naye womuntu siqu kucingo ngaphambi kokuba ujoyine.

Uma Kuvela Isimo Esiphuthumayo: Shayela inombolo yezimo eziphuthumayo yendawo, phuma ngokuthula uye endaweni evulekile ephephile, usize abanye uma ukwazi, futhi ugcine izindlela zokufinyelela zivulekile.

Isimemezelo Sokungabophi: Ukubamba iqhaza emicimbini ye-WorldWideWaves kwenziwa ngokuzithandela nangengozi yakho. Ngokubamba iqhaza, uyavuma ukungafaki zimangalo kubadali bohlelo mayelana nokulimala okungenzeka ngesikhathi somcimbi.

Isaziso Sesikhala Somphakathi: Lona umhlangano womphakathi lapho ukufotwa/ukuthathwa kwamavidiyo yizivakashi noma yabezindaba kungenzeka, ngokuhambisana nemithetho yasendaweni. Asibangi amalungelo esithombe sakho futhi asikwazi ukulawula ukurekhoda kwabantu besithathu. Uma ukhetha ukungaveli, zama ukugwema amakhamera lapho kungenzeka.
Kungani kungekho mcimbi edolobheni lami noma ezweni lami?

Sikhethe amadolobha ambalwa amaningi anabantu abaningi emhlabeni ukuze sakhe igagasi lomhlaba elinencazelo. Izithiyo zobuchwepheshe nezokusebenza okwamanje zisivimba ekusekeleni izindawo ezingenamkhawulo. Sizame ukumela kabanzi amazwekazi, amasiko, nezilimi — okungenakuba kuphelele. Sithemba ukwenezela amanye amadolobha ngokuhamba kwesikhathi.

Sakhe izifulegi zamazwekazi zokuqala, eziyimibono ukusiza ukukhombe masinya amadolobha ohlwini nokukhombisa umoya wobunye okhuthazwa i-WorldWideWaves. Lezi zifulegi aziwona asemthethweni futhi zikhona kuphela kulesi sicelo; azihloselwe ukwehlisa noma ukushintsha izimpawu zikaZwelonke noma zamasiko. Njengoba kungekho zifulegi ezisemthethweni zamazwekazi ezindaweni, siklame ezethu ukuze kube sobala futhi kujabulise. Uma uzithanda, zizwe ukhululekile ukuzisebenzisa.

I-WorldWideWaves umkhankaso wangasese ngokuphelele. Akukho nkampani, inhlangano, noma uhulumeni ongemuva kwawo. Abadali bawo bafuna ukunikeza indlela enokwakha kulabo abazibuza ukuthi bangasiza kanjani ukuthuthukisa umhlaba nezimo zokuphila — umzamo wokulethela ndawonye yonke imizamo ekhona ephambili neyentando yeningi ngaphansi kwephiko elinokuthula, elingezepolitiki.
Cha. Uhlelo lokusebenza lukhululekile ngokuphelele. Nakuba ukwakhiwa nokuthuthukiswa kwalo kudinge isikhathi nemali kubadali, abatholi nzuzo eqondile yezezimali kubo.

Yebo, siyemukela njalo amavolontiya. Ikhodi yomthombo ovulekile ye-app ise-GitHub, futhi ungathinta abadali ku-contact@worldwidewaves.net (izimpendulo azisiqinisekisiwe). Indlela engcono yokusiza ukusabalalisa umlayezo: wabelana ngezithombe namavidiyo emicimbini usebenzisa ama-hashtag aphakanyisiwe, xhumana nabathonya bendawo ukuze nandise umlayezo, xoxa ngakho nomphakathi wakho, futhi okubaluleke kakhulu, joyina igagasi!
Ngingazithola kuphi izindawo engingaya kuzo ngesikhathi semicimbi?
Ungathola uhlu lwezenzo, imisebenzi, nezindawo eziphakanyisiwe ku-https://luma.com/worldwidewaves.

Ubumfihlo bakho bubalulekile kithina. WorldWideWaves yakhelwe ngobumfihlo engqondweni: indawo okuyo ayikaze igcinwe unomphela futhi ayabelwana ngayo nabanye. Siyisebenzisa isikhashana kuphela lapho ubamba iqhaza egagasini, bese isuswa uma uvala uhlelo lokusebenza. Imicimbi oyibeke ezintandokazini igcinwa kudivayisi yakho kuphela. Ukuze uthole imininingwane ephelele yokuthi sivikela kanjani idatha yakho, sicela ufunde Inqubomgomo Yethu Yobumfihlo.

Thepha inkinobho engezansi ukuze uvule imodi yokulingisa. Ezikrinini zomcimbi, sebenzisa inkinobho ethi "play" ekhoneni eliphezulu kwesobunxele lesithombe sendawo ukuze uqale ukulingisa ngezilungiselelo zalo mcimbi (usuku, isikhathi, indawo). Ukumisa ukulingisa, thepha leyo nkinobho efanayo. Ekugcineni, uma usuqedile, phuma kwimodi yokulingisa ngokuthepha isithonjana sokumisa kongqimba oluhlala lubonakala.
Zizwe ukushaya kwesigqi se-Big Apple nge-Independence Day, njengoba igagasi elivuthayo lidlula e-Times Square, e-Central Park, nangaphansi komugqa wesibhakabhaka omide.
Zizwele ubukhazikhazi base-Hollywood, imimoya yase-Pacific, nobuhle obunenkwenkwezi be-L.A. ngesikhathi igagasi elikhanyisa i-City of Angels nge-Independence Day.
Hlonipha i-Mexican Independence Day enhliziyweni ye-CDMX, lapho ubuhle bekoloni buhlangana namandla esimanje, nemilolozelo ye-mariachi iduma ezinkundleni zomlando.
Vumela isigqi se-samba nomoya we-Independence Day kukuphathe udabule i-Paulista Avenue ematasa nezindawo ezinamandla zalo idolobha elikhulu elinezizwe ezixubekile.
Gubha i-Independence yase-Argentina phakathi kwezigqi ze-tango, imigwaqo emikhulu yesitayela saseYurophu, nomoya onothando wama-porteños ogwini lwe-Río de la Plata.
Jabulela umoya wobuningi bezizwe be-Notting Hill Carnival njengoba leli gagasi lidansisa emigwaqweni yomlando, amabhasi aphindwe kabili adumile, kanye ne-Thames engunaphakade.
Ngo-Bastille Day, joyina igagasi eligelezela lisuka e-Eiffel Tower liye e-Champs-Élysées, ligubha uthando nobuciko be-City of Light.
Zizwe umoya wobunye ngo-German Unity Day njengoba igagasi lidlula e-Brandenburg Gate, ezindongeni ezigcwele i-graffiti, nasezakhiweni zesimanje zale nkomfa yenhloko-dolobha enamandla.
NgoSuku Kazwelonke laseSpain, vumela igagasi livuthe izitolo ze-tapas eziphilayo, imigwaqo emikhulu, nelifa lobuciko le-Prado.
Ngo-Ferragosto, hamba namaRoma nezivakashi ezipiazza ezigcwele umculo, imithombo, namandla omgubho agcwalisa i-Eternal City ngaphansi kwelanga lasehlobo.
Zimanzise ngobukhulu be-Red Square ne-Kremlin ngo-Russia Day, njengoba igagasi libonisa umlando wobukhosi ocebile wedolobha nomsindo wesimanje wezizwe ezixubekile.
Gubha i-Republic Day ngegagasi elidlula e-Bosphorus, emasontweni omlando nasemazikwele zesimanje, njengoba i-Istanbul ikhanya ngamaconsathi, amafulegi, neziqhume.
Gubha i-Eid eCairo njengoba imigwaqo nezimakethe zivuka ngezibani zemikhosi, amaphunga amnandi, nemindeni ejabulayo emaka ukuphela kwe-Ramadan ngegagasi elihlanganisayo.
NgoSuku Lenkululeko, joyina igagasi edolobheni leGoli, lapho izakhiwo ezinde zesimanje zihlangana nelifa elicebile lokubekezela nezinhlobonhlobo zamasiko.
Gubha i-Madaraka Day phakathi kwezimakethe eziphilayo nemigwaqo ematasa, lapho impilo yasemadolobheni ihlangana nesango lezilwane zasendle ezimangalisayo zaseKenya.
Wamukela izigqi ze-Afrobeats ngoSuku Lenkululeko laseNigeria, njengoba igagasi lidlula edolobheni elinabantu abaningi e-Afrika nasezimakethe zalo eziphilayo.
NgoSuku Lenkululeko lase-DR Congo, joyina igagasi eligelezela enhlokodolobha enamandla eduze noMfula i-Congo, eligcwele umculo nokuqhosha ngamasiko.
Gubha i-UAE National Day uzungezwe izakhiwo eziphakeme zesimanje, izigodi zesihlabathi, nobukhazikhazi bedolobha lesimanje elihamba phambili emhlabeni.
Khumbula i-Independence yaseNdiya ngomoya we-Bollywood, izakhiwo zenkathi yekoloni, nogu oluthintwe yimvula yeziphepho eceleni koLwandle i-Arabian.
Zizwe umdlandla wobuzwe ngoSuku Lenkululeko njengoba igagasi lidlula imigwaqo emikhulu yenkathi yekoloni, izinqaba zama-Mughal, nenhliziyo yenhloko-dolobha yaseNdiya.
Gubha inkululeko e-Silicon Valley yaseNdiya, lapho amathempeli asendulo ahlangana namapaki ezobuchwepheshe anqamulelayo nesixuku sezizwe ezixubekile esichumayo.
Maka i-Independence Day yase-Indonesia edolobheni elineziqhathaniso ezinkulu, kusukela ezakhiweni ezikhazimulayo kuya ezimakethe zemigwaqo ezimatasa nasezindaweni zefa lamasiko.
Gubha i-National Father’s Day yaseThailand yokuhlonipha uKing Bhumibol e-City of Angels, lapho amathempeli egolide, izimakethe ezintantayo, nokudla komgwaqo okuhle kuvusa izinzwa zakho.
Gubha i-Philippine Independence Day edolobheni lapho ama-jeepney edabula amasonto aseSpanish enkathi yekoloni, izimakethe eziphilayo, nezakhiwo eziphakeme zesimanje.
Joyina izigidi eceleni koMfula i-Sumida njengoba isibhakabhaka sigcwala imibala, nomoya wemikhosi yasehlobo yaseTokyo ubeka isiteji esikahle segagasi elikhazimulayo.
Zimanzise emikhosini ye-Gwangbokjeol njengoba igagasi lidlula ezinqabeni zenkosi, ezikhungweni ze-K-pop, nomugqa wesibhakabhaka ohlanganisa isiko nokuqamba okusha.
Ngo-Labour Day, gibelani igagasi ngamapaki nemigwaqo emikhulu yaseBeijing, lapho izigidi zihlangana khona ukuzulazula, ukwenza i-picnic, nokujabulela umoya weholide lentwasahlobo.
Vumela igagasi lihoshe i-Bund ne-Nanjing Road njengoba iShanghai igubha nemindeni, umculo, namandla ezemikhosi ye-Labour Day.
Zizwe umfutho we-Golden Week yaseHong Kong, njengoba i-Victoria Harbour, izimakethe, nemigwaqo enama-neon kugcwala abantu abagubha i-Labour Day ndawonye.
Gibela igagasi ku-Mardi Gras Parade yaseSydney, lapho i-Oxford Street iqhuma ngemibala yothingo lwenkosazana, ama-float akhangayo, nomoya wekharnivali ohlanganisa amakhulu ezinkulungwane.
Ngo-Melbourne Cup Day, gibela igagasi enhlokodolobha yezamasiko njengoba idolobha ligcwala imigubho nemashi, izixuku ezinamandla ezigqoke kahle, nomoya womkhosi we-'the race that stops a nation'.
Ngo-Canada Day, khukhuleka olwandle olubomvu nolumhlophe njengoba igagasi lidlula e-CN Tower, emiphakathini yezizwe ezixubekile, nasogwini lweLake Ontario.
Gubha i-Canada Day ngasogwini lwe-Pacific, udlule ebuhleni obusuka olwandle buye esibhakabhakeni, ezihlahleni eziluhlaza ze-Stanley Park, nasebuhleni obukhangayo be-downtown.
Ngo-Independence Day, jabulela i-deep-dish nemilingo yezakhiwo ngaseLake Michigan njengoba igagasi lidlula e-Windy City.
Zizwe umoya wenkululeko ngaphansi kobude obudumile be-Golden Gate Bridge, njengoba leli gagasi le-Independence Day lihamba emagqumeni, kuma-cable car, nasemiphakathini ehlukahlukene.
NgoSuku Lenkululeko lase-Peru, hudula ezinkundleni zekoloni, ezindaweni zemivubukulo zangaphambi kwama-Inca, namaphunga amnandi okupheka kwase-Peru okudumile emhlabeni.
Gubha i-Independence yaseColombia phakathi kobuciko bomgwaqo, ukubukwa kwezintaba, nesigqi samiphakathi egcwele i-salsa kule nhloko-dolobha yase-Andes.
Zizwe umdlandla wobuzwe ngoSuku Lenkululeko laseChile njengoba igagasi lihamba ngaphansi kwe-Andes, kumafasadi ekoloni nakumathawula engilazi esimanje.
Joyina i-Sizdah Bedar yaseTehran, usuku lapho imindeni igcwalisa amapaki nezingadi ngama-picnic, ukuhleka, nokuqaleka kabusha, njengoba igagasi lidlula emihlanganweni yangaphandle ephilayo yedolobha.
Gubha i-Independence Day yasePakistan ngasogwini loLwandle i-Arabian, udlule ezimakethe ezimatasa, emlandweni ocebile, nasemandleni ashukumisayo edolobha elikhulu lesizwe.
Kumele sisuke ekulawuleni umonakalo siye ekulungela ukushaqeka. Amazinga okushisa azodlula izinhloso ezibekiwe, ngakho imiphakathi idinga iziqondiso ezicacile, izivivinyo, namathuluzi alula manje.

Lokhu kuqala ngeqiniso elabelwana ngalo. Uhulumeni, izinkampani, nabaholi bomphakathi kufanele baveze amaqiniso ndawonye, bavule idatha, futhi bavumelanise izikhathi ukuze isenzo siqondaniswe, hhayi sihlakazeke.

Ukuze kuvikelwe impilo, kuphishekelwe ukunciphisa ngokuthula izingcindezi zezepolitiki zomhlaba futhi kugxilwe kabusha izinsiza ekusindeni nasekuzinzeni kwabantu.

Buthanani ezingeni eliphezulu namazwe, izinkampani, nabamele umphakathi ukuze kwethulwe iziphakamiso, kwabelwe abaphethe imisebenzi, kubikwe inqubekelaphambili.

Susani izithiyo ngokuvumela izinhlelo zokuhlola, ukuvumelanisa amazinga, nokuxhasa kuqala ukuqina nokufinyeleleka.

Lalelani kubathintekayo bendawo ababhekene nemithelela, nihlele izinsongo ngokubaluleka kanye nabo, nishicilele izinhlelo ngolimi olulula ukuze umphakathi waziswe futhi umenywe ukubamba iqhaza. Ukungasebenzisi udlame, ukubandakanya bonke, ukusobala, nesayensi kuhola lo mzamo.\n\nLungisani nenkathi ezayo: fundisani amakhono asebenzayo, tshalani izimali ezinhlelweni zokuxwayisa kusenesikhathi, ezingqalasizinda eziqinile, nezixazululo ezisekelwe emvelweni, futhi akhani amathuluzi nedatha evulekile yokuhlela komphakathi.
